    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="画布的三种渲染模式"><a href="#画布的三种渲染模式" class="headerlink" title="画布的三种渲染模式"></a>画布的三种渲染模式</h1><p>画布的第一个参数<code>RenderMode</code>的渲染模式有三种：Screen Space-Overlay、Screen Space-Camera以及World Space。</p><h2 id="Screen-Space-Overlay（屏幕控件-覆盖模式）"><a href="#Screen-Space-Overlay（屏幕控件-覆盖模式）" class="headerlink" title="Screen Space-Overlay（屏幕控件-覆盖模式）"></a>Screen Space-Overlay（屏幕控件-覆盖模式）</h2><p>画布会填满整个屏幕空间，并将画布下面的所有的UI元素置于屏幕的最上层，或者说画布的画面永远“覆盖”其他普通的3D画面，如果屏幕尺寸被改变，画布将自动改变尺寸来匹配屏幕</p><p>此模式只适合单纯的UI开发，比如游戏的排行榜，游戏结束之后的界面，并且会自动适应屏幕大小，但是要注意，所谓的适应屏幕，不是说你把图片设置到摄像机所显示游戏的界面一样大，他就会自动适应。必须把组件设置为全部边自动拉伸才行</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="Screen-Space-Camera（屏幕空间-摄影机模式）"><a href="#Screen-Space-Camera（屏幕空间-摄影机模式）" class="headerlink" title="Screen Space-Camera（屏幕空间-摄影机模式）"></a>Screen Space-Camera（屏幕空间-摄影机模式）</h2><p>需要将画布设置为Screen Space-Camera模式后添加渲染摄像机</p><p>和Screen Space-Overlay模式类似，画布也是填满整个屏幕空间，如果屏幕尺寸改变，画布也会自动改变尺寸来匹配屏幕。所不同的是，在该模式下，画布会被放置到摄影机前方。在这种渲染模式下，画布看起来 绘制在一个与摄影机固定距离的平面上。所有的UI元素都由该摄影机渲染，因此摄影机的设置会影响到UI画面。在此模式下，UI元素是由perspective也就是视角设定的，视角广度由Filed of View设置。</p><p>　　这种模式可以用来实现在UI上显示3D模型的需求，比如很多MMO游戏中的查看人物装备的界面，可能屏幕的左侧有一个运动的3D人物，左侧是一些UI元素。通过设置Screen Space-Camera模式就可以实现上述的需求，效果如下图所示：</p><p>对于Order in Layer，可以理解为栈，先进去的后显示，后进去的先显示。也就是说，数值越大，就越靠前，这个模式需要单独的渲染摄像机，这也是大多数游戏所使用的渲染模式，如果游戏元素不多，可以把Main Camera设置为渲染相机，否则就单独创建一个相机用于渲染。</p><h2 id="World-Space世界控件模式"><a href="#World-Space世界控件模式" class="headerlink" title="World Space世界控件模式"></a>World Space世界控件模式</h2><p>在此模式下，画布被视为与场景中其他普通游戏对象性质相同的类似于一张面片（Plane）的游戏物体。画布的尺寸可以通过<code>RectTransform</code>设置，所有的UI元素可能位于普通3D物体的前面或者后面显示。当UI为场景的一部分时，可以使用这个模式。</p><p>　　它有一个单独的参数Event Camera，用来指定接受事件的摄像机，可以通过画布上的<code>GraphicRaycaster</code>组件发射射线产生事件。</p><p>　　这种模式可以用来实现跟随人物移动的血条或者名称</p><h1 id="鼠标坐标转化为摄像机模式坐标"><a href="#鼠标坐标转化为摄像机模式坐标" class="headerlink" title="鼠标坐标转化为摄像机模式坐标"></a>鼠标坐标转化为摄像机模式坐标</h1><figure class="highlight c#"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">OnDrag</span>(<span class="params">PointerEventData eventData</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//【如果的是画布的第一种模式：Overlay】拖拽图片</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//transform.position = Input.mousePosition;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        Vector3 worldPos = Vector3.zero;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//【如果的是画布的第二种模式：Camera】拖拽图片</span></span><br><span class="line">        RectTransformUtility.</span><br><span class="line">            ScreenPointToWorldPointInRectangle(</span><br><span class="line">                transform.root <span class="keyword">as</span> RectTransform,<span class="comment">//画布</span></span><br><span class="line">                Input.mousePosition,<span class="comment">//屏幕坐标</span></span><br><span class="line">                Camera.main,<span class="comment">//渲染摄像机</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">out</span> worldPos);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">         //设置当前UI的世界坐标</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">         transform.position = worldPos;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">         Vector2 translatePoint2 = Vector2.zero;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">         //将屏幕坐标转换为UI中的本地坐标</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">         RectTransformUtility.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">         ScreenPointToLocalPointInRectangle(</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">         transform.parent as RectTransform,//⽗对象的RectTransform</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">         Input.mousePosition,//屏幕坐标</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">         Camera.main,//当前画布模式中选择的渲染摄像机</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">         out translatePoint2);//输⼊结果</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">         //设置本地坐标</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">         transform.localPosition = translatePoint2;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">      */</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="UGUI回调函数"><a href="#UGUI回调函数" class="headerlink" title="UGUI回调函数"></a>UGUI回调函数</h1><p><img src="/../images/image-20221016212922850.png" alt="image-20221016212922850"></p><h1 id="场景异步加载"><a href="#场景异步加载" class="headerlink" title="场景异步加载"></a>场景异步加载</h1><p><code>AsyncOperation</code></p><p><img src="/../images/image-20221016213257918.png" alt="image-20221016213257918"></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">SceneManager.LoadSceneAsync(&quot;场景名字&quot;);   异步加载场景  返回 AsyncOperation   </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">allowSceneActivation     是否允许场景加载完成后展示</span><br><span class="line">progress                 场景加载进度，到0.9就已经加载完成</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="unity中的单例"><a href="#unity中的单例" class="headerlink" title="unity中的单例"></a>unity中的单例</h1><h2 id="单例类"><a href="#单例类" class="headerlink" title="单例类"></a>单例类</h2><p>需要存储跨场景信息时使用</p><p>不继承<code>MonoBehaviour</code></p><p>优点：不受切换场景的影响</p><h2 id="单例脚本"><a href="#单例脚本" class="headerlink" title="单例脚本"></a>单例脚本</h2><p>当前场景中唯一的一个脚本组件，只能挂载在一个游戏对象上</p><p>优点 ：跨场景时将会被销毁 </p><p>  避免被销毁的方法：<code>DontDestroyOnLoad(gameObject)</code></p><figure class="highlight c#"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">ShopButton</span> : <span class="title">MonoBehaviour</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//单例脚本对象</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> ShopButton instance;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Awake</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//获取单例</span></span><br><span class="line">        instance = <span class="keyword">this</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//阻止切换场景时，销毁当前对象</span></span><br><span class="line">        DontDestroyOnLoad(gameObject);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Update</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//当按下空格键切换场景</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(Input.GetKeyDown(KeyCode.Space))</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">//切换场景</span></span><br><span class="line">            UnityEngine.SceneManagement.SceneManager.LoadScene(<span class="string">&quot;Sprite2D&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//其他游戏对象可使用此脚本</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Buy</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Debug.Log(<span class="string">&quot;Buy&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="简单2d动画"><a href="#简单2d动画" class="headerlink" title="简单2d动画"></a>简单2d动画</h1><p>创建 <code>Animator Contriller</code> 在其中添加 <code>Animation Clip</code> </p><p>将sprite 放在动画中 设置Samples (每秒播放帧数)</p><h1 id="2d碰撞"><a href="#2d碰撞" class="headerlink" title="2d碰撞"></a>2d碰撞</h1><p><img src="/../images/image-20221016191709002.png" alt="image-20221016191709002"></p><p>回调函数</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">OnCollisionEnter2D(Collision2D)  开始碰撞</span><br><span class="line">OnCollisionStay2D(Collision2D)   碰撞ing</span><br><span class="line">OnCollisionExit2D(Collision2D)   结束碰撞</span><br><span class="line">OnTriggerEnter2D(Collider2D) </span><br><span class="line">OnTriggerStay2D(Collider2D)</span><br><span class="line">OnTriggerExit2D(Collider2D)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="摄像机"><a href="#摄像机" class="headerlink" title="摄像机"></a>摄像机</h1><p><img src="/../images/image-20221016211612486.png" alt="image-20221016211612486"></p><h1 id="设置小地图"><a href="#设置小地图" class="headerlink" title="设置小地图"></a>设置小地图</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">新建 Render Texture  将新建的 Render Texture 拖动到小地图摄像机上 </span><br><span class="line">将摄像机视图设置为正交视图， 将纹理图片放到UI界面的图片上，可以设置按钮，控制摄像机的范围，来控制小地图的大小 </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>按钮点击事件</code></p><figure class="highlight c#"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">onchick</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">float</span> res = camera.GetComponent&lt;Camera&gt;().orthographicSize;</span><br><span class="line">        res += fl;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (res &gt; <span class="number">10f</span>) res = <span class="number">10f</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (res &lt; <span class="number">1f</span>) res = <span class="number">1f</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        camera.GetComponent&lt;Camera&gt;().orthographicSize = res;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="3D动画"><a href="#3D动画" class="headerlink" title="3D动画"></a>3D动画</h1><h2 id="3D模型"><a href="#3D模型" class="headerlink" title="3D模型"></a>3D模型</h2><p><img src="/../images/image-20221016201004872.png" alt="image-20221016201004872"></p><p><code>3D模型动画类型</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">None  无动画</span><br><span class="line">Legacy  旧版动画</span><br><span class="line">Generic    非人形动画</span><br><span class="line">Humanoid   人型动画</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>3D模型骨骼</code></p><p><img src="/../images/image-20221016201458424.png" alt="image-20221016201458424"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;画布的三种渲染模式&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#画布的三种渲染模式&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;画布的三种渲染模式&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;画布的三种渲染模式&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;画布的第一个参数&lt;code&gt;RenderMode&lt;/code&gt;的渲染模式有三种：Screen Space-Overlay、Screen Space-Camera以及World Space。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;Screen-Space-Overlay（屏幕控件-覆盖模式）&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Screen-Space-Overlay（屏幕控件-覆盖模式）&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Screen Space-Overlay（屏幕控件-覆盖模式）&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Screen Space-Overlay（屏幕控件-覆盖模式）&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;画布会填满整个屏幕空间，并将画布下面的所有的UI元素置于屏幕的最上层，或者说画布的画面永远“覆盖”其他普通的3D画面，如果屏幕尺寸被改变，画布将自动改变尺寸来匹配屏幕&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;此模式只适合单纯的UI开发，比如游戏的排行榜，游戏结束之后的界面，并且会自动适应屏幕大小，但是要注意，所谓的适应屏幕，不是说你把图片设置到摄像机所显示游戏的界面一样大，他就会自动适应。必须把组件设置为全部边自动拉伸才行&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
